{"tid":1075783,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"百屌牛師傅去左y記","createTime":"2019-03-24T11:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T12:49:06.000Z","uid":5551,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e54d41e7660818fb8af7655df827bda4ef9dc23b","tid":1075783,"uid":5551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"如題 <br />\n有無人證實到？<br />\n聽人講佢無學生 連車都供唔到 賣身去y記"},{"pid":"58b70efeb4da45725ed4e55ca115912fab00f0b4","tid":1075783,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:41:47.000Z","msg":"跟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽佢講佢個schedule好爆"},{"pid":"798e156bca85169a6f04f54d027da11f874f1fee","tid":1075783,"uid":5551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"58b70efeb4da45725ed4e55ca115912fab00f0b4","tid":1075783,"uid":101289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:41:47.000Z","msg":"跟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽佢講佢個schedule好爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"佢成日都話自己好多人跟佢學架啦<br />\n但就周圍R學生  回佣"},{"pid":"1758fad34d91eb0128a5854ea23e71ecd76936b9","tid":1075783,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:55:25.000Z","msg":"連登應該冇咩人識百屌成材牛師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eabdd1b1e30cef0b98edc3a680e9205ff8c874","tid":1075783,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"法國佬"},{"pid":"d7a96fbe110d1ac1366e2c2c6c186a147a0e4c28","tid":1075783,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:16:33.000Z","msg":"午帥傳"},{"pid":"33a044dd40e8406d192cf2a639b63212adc11f31","tid":1075783,"uid":48623,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"應該大把傻鳩中伏，當初一開始話自己教得幾好幾好，再搵多一兩個打手吹奏下。成班傻仔爭住搵佢，前後比人爆左幾次遲到、鳩屌、呃鐘都算。<br />\n最爆係有次有個舊生係高登到開 Post 直線屌鳩佢，故事大約係話個學生跟佢比佢鳩屌都算，個學生頂唔順就話想轉師大，條友扮曬野彈佢比其他師傅，但個學生發現左佢叫個新師傅教到佢肥佬報復。呢個一石激起千層浪，成個 Post 忽然彈左勁多中伏同巴打。有巴打試過考試個日比佢放飛機，又有巴打上親佢堂條友都會中途去痾屎消失三個字，又有大量巴打比佢燥狂行為嚇親，仲有巴打話試過開佢波之後就即場死狗。<br />\n估唔到而家又有人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8d0a1c368479b2d9674cf91eafe2f95e7bd4db","tid":1075783,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"跟出面師傅學車都戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"d8a1a491ae86244413ac22b0ab6179fa1cc5ac1a","tid":1075783,"uid":28459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"果時話搵佢學車 , 比左料佢幫我報名 報筆試<br />\n之後搵左第個師傅學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3084db52ba9157adf3ac8360b947bafc799c5c15","tid":1075783,"uid":108948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"好多年前搵過佢試堂，垃撚圾。淨係識屌唔識教，架車又廢到喊，上左兩堂就無上"},{"pid":"5d14bb18804f4e6613401732b5bb928b81030be6","tid":1075783,"uid":38047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mnw1yljf4ZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMnw1yljf4ZY&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8gomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=348ae370\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mnw1yljf4ZY</a>"},{"pid":"65f72032600e2ea4b614c4d001351e37691deca1","tid":1075783,"uid":89801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:53:01.000Z","msg":"六年前跟佢學車<br />\n雖然佢成日遲到 遲到又藉多多（例如係停車場攞車比人頂住左出唔到車，聲稱踩狗屎去左買拖鞋）<br />\n教車態度又真係麻麻<br />\n<br />\n但我跟佢只係學左五日車就合格左<br />\n<br />\n當年應該160蚊咁上下價錢<br />\n5日10堂=1600蚊<br />\n租車好似1300咁上下<br />\n加埋學牌 考試費 1058<br />\n四千蚊考到牌 算係幾平"},{"pid":